{"tid":1578033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家做好十一文宣先講啦 唔好浪費時間人民鬥人民","createTime":"2019-09-18T03:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T18:39:35.000Z","uid":172093,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"539857708de31b33ee570b3a23e864c0749c83cf","tid":1578033,"uid":172093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:40:02.000Z","msg":"根本宜家有好多重點要繼續煲大<br />\n721 831 新屋嶺 呢三單全部要繼續發掘資料<br />\n民主與人權法案又要繼續文宣<br />\n十一又已經臨近 而文宣又未開始做<br />\n敵人已經夠多 支那 狗 鄉黑  福建仔<br />\n班垃圾廢佬藍絲咪由鳩佢係屋企打飛機<br />\n呢班垃圾宜家都唔夠膽出黎㗎啦<br />\n咁我地就無謂去挑釁班垃圾 增加敵人<br />\n所以我真係唔建議玩咩圍馬場<br />\n不如諗下有咩新既方法做文宣好過<br />\n連儂 國歌 人鏈全部都好好<br />\n要connect世界 要做既係更加有創意既示威<br />\n係好撚左膠 不過人地鬼佬真係受呢套<br />\n要記住一點 有文宣下既勇武可以係正義<br />\n而冇文宣下既勇武只係暴力同破壞"},{"pid":"329afb38b751913f41879e7dcfb508601a2c72cf","tid":1578033,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"414ff6b0fde64d6196e2fc893674b79a2a4fb6da","tid":1578033,"uid":290443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> agger"},{"pid":"728c53ababfda699c2b8464ad3e2c31dae12fcdc","tid":1578033,"uid":73988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:47:09.000Z","msg":"賀佢生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc9a868978e9253c256bba68d02dfcfe73b0accb","tid":1578033,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:47:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57438b97d066b25cc2051a0e4c4b23118cf0f6f4","tid":1578033,"uid":254645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:48:17.000Z","msg":"agger <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.